<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GmUtoye.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGmUtoye.jpg&h=36d1db08&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1gBzi6w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1gBzi6w.jpg&h=067ee06f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n堅持五大訴求，不撤不散︰<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一、撤回修例<br />\n二、撤回6.12暴動定性<br />\n三、撤銷所有反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n四、責成獨立調查委員會追究警方濫暴<br />\n五、實行真雙普選"},{"pid":"50b6656d9f3d55ab340d329def1f0138f5fc7c76","tid":1312892,"uid":69525,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T15:34:18.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">14/7 聽日一齊去沙田野餐。\n\n唔理你和理非定勇武派 \n請帶齊裝備保護自己\n另外 聽日好曬 一人一長遮\n-\n警方定性612為暴動 繼續追擊警方濫權\n要求成立獨立調查委員會\n繼續五大訴求\n-\n大家繼續努力</code></pre>"},{"pid":"cd62526d3cdd568ed09e0a3be3a058f687b5b4e4","tid":1312892,"uid":136811,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T15:35:01.000Z","msg":"我今日去上水<br />\n聽日去沙田"},{"pid":"db2593c95785320ea66b33e8e5eaa6c856324cf6","tid":1312892,"uid":26846,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"9bd9b649a3a19359352a3913a0dd13f44c3292ea","tid":1312892,"uid":136811,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e4b361bd0faf7d041e9cc5f8bca9ff28e00368e3","tid":1312892,"uid":26846,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T15:30:56.000Z","msg":"講真 可以點 大家未有革命心態"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T15:32:24.000Z","msg":"理論上係要長期抗爭 但我地應該等唔切"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T15:35:11.000Z","msg":"唔係話失敗主義 講真呀你叫 唔好交稅呀都冇人理啦 200萬人 200萬人唔交稅政府收皮啦使鬼搞咁多嘢咩 事實就係大部分人都係喺度隔岸觀火 嚟嚟去去都係嗰班人抗爭 所以你話邊有得搞 你冇外力協助其實係真係冇得搞呀老老實實"},{"pid":"b64d7588f8a3a44c88caf89554d650595555416b","tid":1312892,"uid":54921,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T15:36:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51ecee69777b9dc8160bf0b86b62050603fe131e","tid":1312892,"uid":136257,"like